10
00:01:02,929 --> 00:01:06,933
{\an8}<i>A grand show to further their careers has
been made for them to perform in spring.</i>

11
00:01:09,135 --> 00:01:14,407
{\an8}I hope to take the audience into the world
of ultimate Japanese entertainment.

12
00:01:14,908 --> 00:01:16,009
{\an8}MINAMIZA THEATRE

13
00:01:16,076 --> 00:01:19,079
{\an8}<i>The first stage on which they'll perform
in this endeavor</i>

14
00:01:19,379 --> 00:01:21,748
{\an8}<i>will be in the birthplace
of Kabuki, Kyoto.</i>

15
00:01:24,017 --> 00:01:27,387
{\an8}<i>The name of the show is</i>
Takizawa Kabuki ZERO.

16
00:01:28,688 --> 00:01:33,426
{\an8}<i>In the short time they've had to prepare,
they've had to overcome many high hurdles.</i>

17
00:01:34,794 --> 00:01:36,696
Nice smiles, please!

18
00:01:38,064 --> 00:01:41,868
{\an8}<i>More than anything, this has called for
an even deeper sense of unity.</i>

19
00:01:42,769 --> 00:01:43,903
{\an8}<i>POTATO</i> MAGAZINE SHOOT

20
00:01:43,970 --> 00:01:46,639
{\an8}<i>To give Snow Man a power-up,</i>

21
00:01:46,706 --> 00:01:49,142
{\an8}<i>an additional three members
have been added,</i>

22
00:01:49,209 --> 00:01:51,444
{\an8}<i>making them a unit of nine.</i>

23
00:01:51,511 --> 00:01:53,213
{\an8}3 NEW MEMBERS TURN 6 TO 9

24
00:01:53,279 --> 00:01:56,816
{\an8}I think what we have to do now is
actually try out all kinds of things.

25
00:01:57,250 --> 00:02:00,854
{\an8}Surely we need to explore, right?
Now that there's nine of us.

26
00:02:02,522 --> 00:02:07,994
